mer said austin  her guidance will be instrumental as we continue to build upon our capabilities to deliver value to thousands of brands and retailers as well as to consumers delivering the valuable content they need to make informed purchase decisions wherever and whenever they need it  bazaarvoice is an innovative company that is well positioned to expand upon its market leadership in leveraging consumer generated content to improve brand strength business performance and bottom line results said ritzcovan  i am excited to be a part of the team as we work with both current clients and new prospects to deliver that content through even more products services and channels ritzcovan brings to bazaarvoice more than  years of print digital media and software sales experience with industry leading organizations  most recently ritzcovan served as the global chief revenue officer at sizmek a leading open ad management platform company for multiscreen campaigns a role preceded by her tenure as chief revenue officer at parade media group  prior to that she served as vice president strategy and marketing solutions at yahoo inc and earlier served as vice president corporate sales and marketing digital for time inc  ritzcovan started her career in print media where she held a number of roles with conde nast publications miller publishing and h  h publishing if you liked this article you might like week ahead jobs report takes center stage ahead of feds december meeting the us labor market is back in the spotlight in the coming week with the nonfarm payrolls report on tap for a friday morning release keris alison lahiff nov    am est bazaarvoice bv stock sharply higher after q results top estimates bazaarvoice bv reported betterthanexpected results for the  fiscal first quarter late wednesday kaya yurieff sep    pm edt insider trading alert  wlfc bv and afop traded by insiders stocks with insider trader activity include wlfc bv and afop thestreet wire apr    am edt bazaarvoice 