 clients and driving growth across the board ritzcovan will join the company as of december   she will be based out of new york sizmeks center of operations reporting directly to sizmeks ceo and president neil nguyen media contact dana miller tel  presssizmekcom related articles other press releases by sizmek inc sizmek to acquire rocket fuel creating industry’s first predictive omnichannel marketing platform serving agencies and brands july    sizmek addresses cross media plan optimization introduces serverlevel crossdsp frequency capping july    sizmek adds digital audio channel to ad server provides buyers with access to programmatic audio through strikead dsp june    sizmek announces chief data officer may    sizmek appoints dr mark grether as executive chairman february     other news releases in directors and officers in the last  days profile sizmek inc   subscribe via rss  subscribe via atom  javascript austin texas united states   httpwwwsizmekcom contact data media contact dana miller tel  presssizmekcom contact with a reader account its easy to send email directly to the contact for this release sign up today for your free reader account already have an account log in here media files liz ritzcovan jpeg   x  image url  copy the link below liz ritzcovan appointed cro at sizmek formats available original large medium small sizmek inc logo logo url  copy the link below formats available original medium small tags advertising management changes newswire distribution network  management home newsroom rss feeds legal contact us about us globenewswire a nasdaq company is one of the worlds largest newswire distribution networks specializing in the delivery of corporate press releases financial disclosures and multimedia content to the media investment community individual investors and the general public contact us corporate headquarters  rosecrans avenue suite  el segundo ca  phone   fax   european headquarters woolgate exchange  basinghall street london ecv ha 